node.accessibility_caption: Photo by TOOTYMCNOOTY aka. Lulu on July 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Student ID: 1700080/2 Award: Bachelor of Arts with Honours Illustration Class: First Class Honours'.

node.text:
Hey everyone, it’s been a while!

Some of you know that I’ve been studying Illustration at University whilst I do a lot of Animation work online, well today I got my final grade back which is a First, the highest honour you can get (I think????? Idk at this point) and I couldn’t be any more surprised!

If I’m going to be honest, I never knew I would get this kind of grade in the first place due to my mental health really breaking down as this year progressed, I planned to create another animation along with “Life of a Phrog” which I handed in but couldn’t conjure up the energy during that time, so I handed in an animation and an animatic, something I wish I could have finished and never felt like it was complete. During these last months I haven’t been able to create things like I used to, it has been really hard to even think creatively when someone so close to you is suffering with a rare long-term illness.

However, receiving this result today has reminded me how much I’ve done creatively for you guys over the last two years and most importantly what I REALLY want to be doing in life, even though I still have my flaws and things to learn still I am happy that both University and Social Media has pushed me into a pathway I want to go in.

I’ve still got a bit to go before I go back to being my regular self as I’m about to move again, but now that University is out of the way I can really focus on what I want to be doing, which is creating silly animations for you guys to watch!!

Thank you @inspiredaub for my 4 years here, it’s been a decent rollercoaster~ 🎺🐸
